history.content:
The College of Letters and Science presents... 
SAVE YOUR SEMESTER WORKSHOP

Get help navigating the options and resources available
to you if you're worried about grades! This workshop
covers L&S policies on grading option changes (P/NP), late
change petitions, incomplete grades, and withdrawal.
We'll also cover campus resources.
